snippet.title: DOOM: Bethesda E3 Showcase Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description:
Pre-order DOOM today! http://doom.com/en-us/preorder

The worldwide debut of DOOM from Bethesda's #BE3 Showcase. 

Join id Software's Marty Stratton as he walks the audience through the game's single-player, multiplayer, and revolutionary SnapMap mode.

For more DOOM videos, check our our YouTube playlist
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLB60F5590E713F60F

For news and updates on DOOM, visit these sites.
Official Website – DOOM.com
Twitter – Twitter.com/DOOM
Facebook – Facebook.com/DOOM
Instagram – Instagram.com/DOOM_Game
